        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "最高級の和牛は、赤身と白身のバランスが絶妙な霜降り状態になっている。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「見てくれよ、この見事な霜降り！今日は奮発してステーキを焼くぞ」。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "あまりに霜降りがきつい肉は、年を重ねるごとに胃にもたれるようになってきた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 3,
        "gloss": "(of fish, chicken, shellfish, etc.) blanching by exposure to boiling and then icy water",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "鶏肉をサッと熱湯にくぐらせる霜降りのひと手間で、余計な脂と臭みが抜ける。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "白身魚の皮目を霜降りにすることで、見た目も美しく食感も良くなる。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "「煮物を作る前に、まずはこの牛肉を霜降りにしてください」と料理講師が指導した。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 4,
        "gloss": "formation of frost",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "今朝は冷え込んだせいか、野菊の葉の上にうっすらと霜降りが降りていた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "車のフロントガラスに霜降りが生じ、出勤前に霜を取る作業に追われた。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "一面に霜降りが広がる銀世界の景色は、冬の朝だけの特別な贈り物だ。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
